## When unsure

1. If it is **genre-specific gameplay** → **ccs-survival**, not `ccs-framework`
2. If it benefits **all games** → upstream PR to **ccs-framework**
3. If it needs **global singleton or scene scan** → redesign to explicit registration
4. Run **`SCN_CCS_Bootstrap`** smoke tests with diagnostics enabled after Core changes
